      <blockquote>
       <p>
        Prototype and development parts can be designed or made to order, particularly millimetre wave guide components. One-off or short batch turned components can also be undertaken.
       </p>
       <p>
        I specialise in the design and construction of very small spring probe PCB test jigs. These can be made very quickly either to a PCB drawing or from the PCB itself.
        <br />
        <br />
        During my time in industry I was called upon many times to design and construct presentation pieces, both for exhibition use and for retirement gifts. I can produce a special sectioned version of your product and mount it under an exhibition glass dome.
        <br />
        <br />
        I can help you whenever your own machine shop considers that something is too small for them to make.
       </p>
       <p>
